-- Project Euler #30: Digit Fifth Powers
-- Sum of all numbers equal to the sum of fifth powers of their digits
-- Answer: 443839

0 'total let
2 'n let
(n 354295 lt)
(
  n 's let
  0 'dsum let
  (s 0 gt)
  (
    s 10 mod 'd let
    d d mul d mul d mul d mul dsum plus 'dsum let
    s 10 div 's let
  ) while
  dsum n eq (total n plus 'total let) () if
  n 1 plus 'n let
) while
total print
